dct_title_s: New Jersey - Cape May County - Ocean City - Emergency dune protection sections II
dct_description_sm: Map of Ocean City covering area from 59th Street to 42nd Street. Map shows soundings, pilings, the edge of Berm, groins, and the condition of piers and bulkhead. Drainage ditches, Peck Beach, and marsh areas are located on the map. Attached are sheets 27 A and 27 B.
